        <title locale="en_US">&lt;i&gt;Certhiasomus&lt;/i&gt;, a new genus of woodcreeper (Aves: Passeriformes: Dendrocolaptidae)</title>
        <abstract locale="en_US">Phylogenetic analysis of the family Dendrocolaptidae (Aves: Passeriformes) indicates that the two species traditionally placed in the genus &lt;i&gt;Deconychura&lt;/i&gt; are not sister taxa. &lt;i&gt;Certhiasomus,&lt;/i&gt; a new genus of woodcreeper, is described for one of these species, &lt;i&gt;C.&lt;/i&gt; &lt;i&gt;stictolaemus.&lt;/i&gt;</abstract>
